                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- Text I belongs to the so-called "Ḥayq recension" of Gadla Takla Hāymānot. Cp. Mss. BN Éth. 342 (GrébGriaule II, 18-20), Ṭānāsee 162 (SixTana III, 202-06), BN Éth. 697 (uncatalogued, see C. CONTI-ROSSINI, 1910, “I principali studi pubblicati in occasione della missione Duchesne-Fournet in Abissinia (manoscritti etiopici e ricerche antropologiche)”, Bolletino della Societa Geografica Italiana ser. 4, 11: 1<ref type="mss" corresp="ES060107">060-107</ref>1.). For a French translation of the text s. J. DUCHESNE-FOURNET, Mission en Éthiopie, 1<ref type="mss" corresp="ES901190">901-190</ref>3, vol. 1, Paris 1908,<ref type="mss" corresp="ES340431">340-431</ref>.</note>
                     <note>- Text I included the embedded colophon of the Vita: [<locus target="#129rb">129rb</locus>, l.16] ወይእዚኒ፡ ንነግረክሙ፡ ዘተከሥተ፡ መ [<locus target="#129va">129va</locus>] ጽሐፈ፡ ገድሉ፡ ለክቡር፡ ብእሲ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አቡነ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ በ፪፻ወ፯ዓመተ፡ ወ፱አውራኃ፡ ተከሥተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ በ፯ትውልድ፡ በከመ፡ እምአዳም፡ እስከ፡ ወልደ፡ ያሬድ፡ ወአርአዮ፡ ሄኖክ፡ ፊደለ፡ በጸፍጸፈ፡ ሰማይ፡ ዘይብል፡ አልፋ፡ ወኦ[ሜጋ]፡ የውጣ፡ ወቤጣ፡ ወበከመ፡ ከሠተ፡ ሎቱ፡ በ፯ትውልድ፡ እምነ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ እስከ፡ እስከ፡[sic] ዮሓንስ፡ ከመ፡[sic] (…) [<locus target="#129vb">129vb</locus>, l.17] ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ በ፸ወ፯ [<locus target="#130ra">130ra</locus>] ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ በመንግሥተ፡ ገብረ፡ መስቀል፡ መፍቀሬ፡ እግዚአብሔር።</note>
